Package com.pump.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CombinedInputStream
    This is a combination of multiple InputStreams.
    ConsoleLogger
    This logs the System.err and System.out streams to a text file.
    CsvParser
    This is simple parser for CSV files.
    DuplexWriter
    This Writer channels data to multiple writers.
    FileLogger
    This logs text to a file.
    FileTreeIterator
    This iterates through a file tree structure.
    GuardedInputStream
    This filtered stream places an initial limit on the number of bytes that can be read.
    GuardedOutputStream
    This restricts the amount of data that can be written to an underlying OutputStream.
    HTMLEncoding
    This class can encode and decode over 200 HTML references.
    IOUtils
    A collection of static methods relating to Files and IO operations.
    LookAheadReader
    This reads data but also provides a couple of convenient .peek() methods to look ahead.
    MeasuredInputStream
    This InputStream relays information from an underlying InputStream while measuring how many bytes have been read or skipped.
    MeasuredOutputStream
    This OutputStream passes information along to an underlying OutputStream while counting how many bytes are written.
    NullOutputStream
    This OutputStream does not write any data.
    SuffixFilenameFilter
    A file filter that is based on a suffix.
    Token
    A basic text token from a parsed line of text.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CsvParser.ParseException  
    ParserException
    This is an exception related to a poorly formed Token.
